## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all potential barriers to community involvement in research. Additionally, the search was limited to sources available up to October 2023, and newer insights or developments may not be included. The context of each study or report may vary, affecting the generalizability of the findings. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the barriers to community involvement in research.

